-- Everest Re Says Superstorm Sandy May Cost It $220 Million
-- B y   Z a c h a r y   T r a c e r
-- 2012-12-20T21:12:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-20/everest-re-says-superstorm-sandy-may-cost-it-220-million.html
Everest Re Group Ltd., the Bermuda-
based insurer and reinsurer, said losses from superstorm Sandy
are about $220 million.  The figure is after taxes and fueled by reinsurance,
Everest Re said today in a statement distributed by Business
Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
